{"tid":1399067,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3警守投訴課入口稱唔係呢度　譚文豪捉正　警長抄警員編號再跟進","createTime":"2019-08-03T04:36:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T06:23:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8618aecd3ad0b1e53a8a9f79559def9415de7644","tid":1399067,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3114632/org/0bca5ddc8065625eb277996c53c61493.jpg/11JqrtN-IVU1Ler-O9yLMDSq0gNqBimjZebXQWXm10E?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3114632%2Forg%2F0bca5ddc8065625eb277996c53c61493.jpg%2F11JqrtN-IVU1Ler-O9yLMDSq0gNqBimjZebXQWXm10E%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=0aebcd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n譚文豪在fb分享今午在其身上發生的不可思議事件。他指今日就警員濫暴同委任證問題去灣仔警總投訴警察課落口供，已非首次到場的他，熟路地走到警總堅偉樓附翼地下投訴警察報案中心，惟在入口卻見3名警員企正門口守着，他稱禮貌性問對方「呢個係咪投訴警察課入口」，但「警員更確鑿地回答唔係，亦阻止我進入。」<br />\n<br />\n網民笑中有淚：若要人不知，唔好咁低B！<br />\n<br />\n明知非事實的譚文豪，即時致電與他約好落口供的投訴課何警長，他指何在這個被稱為不是投訴課入口的入口走出來，並向他確認有關入口就是前往投訴警察報案中心，何亦指不知道有關警員為何在該入口站崗並誤導市民，她其後入內請一名鄭姓警長處理，譚文豪即向鄭表明要向這3名警員作出投訴。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪稱：「唔通3位駐守灣仔警總嘅警員會唔知自己站崗守緊咩？我呼籲警方唔好試圖阻攔巿民行使公民權利投訴濫權警察，咁做只會引起反效果。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3114629/org/cac6cbf314ecc27abeb712978c6c7035.jpg/635pEXC5K2rrVjmwEOxNsWPYE7VRQaesKo91bCqPdWw?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3114629%2Forg%2Fcac6cbf314ecc27abeb712978c6c7035.jpg%2F635pEXC5K2rrVjmwEOxNsWPYE7VRQaesKo91bCqPdWw%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=123af174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為免市民誤會，譚文豪特別拍下真投訴課入口照片，讓大家認清。（譚文豪fb）<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/359510/3%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4%E8%AA%B2%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%A3%E7%A8%B1%E5%94%94%E4%BF%82%E5%91%A2%E5%BA%A6-%E8%AD%9A%E6%96%87%E8%B1%AA%E6%8D%89%E6%AD%A3-%E8%AD%A6%E9%95%B7%E6%8A%84%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%B7%A8%E8%99%9F%E5%86%8D%E8%B7%9F%E9%80%B2</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a6fba01f2383986b032623621d90687d64f4e11d","tid":1399067,"uid":23808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"冇一個黑警係無辜"},{"pid":"9e78634f52ac5559b677f88e63e282684b49e319","tid":1399067,"uid":6889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"自己攞嚟衰"},{"pid":"026ddb104b3bd6480626cfc76adade4227a90466","tid":1399067,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770c4123daf3ac027e95914a30ef1a8c7e28b045","tid":1399067,"uid":131980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1167b60f8fd9621a9bbde4744fad391d03604553","tid":1399067,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8f4f1b323daa29cd5ec9b00b87f52feb45557a","tid":1399067,"uid":243491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:41:54.000Z","msg":"真係好弱智"},{"pid":"fbc0db6e192712c241244e3aed8265021e78f03c","tid":1399067,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:41:55.000Z","msg":"傻散<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4b4dee7f565d6054df1029823cc61fda778e18","tid":1399067,"uid":2007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"柒警無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe2d8fd8a3d06492bd65f763716cfafd3a0bed8","tid":1399067,"uid":6889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:44:15.000Z","msg":"啱啱畢業連柴都未有，今次真係有排都無<img sr